title: Default RedHat Install of IceHouse fails

comments.content:
When following the deployment guide for RedHat IceHouse install the nova compute layer fails to launch a vm via the dashboard.

I am running CentOs 6.4.

Acutally.  I finally found my error.  I missed configuring the neutron connection information in the nova.conf file. 

You can close this issue as it was not a bug.
